        <Parent_String>shelly limestone [300011300], fossiliferous limestone [300011288], limestone by composition: aggregate type [300011287], limestone by composition [300137624], limestone [300011286], carbonate rock [300011283], sedimentary rock by composition [300011274], sedimentary rock [300011273], rock (inorganic material) [300011692], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
